   <p id="Par95" class="p">Finally, using Eq. 
    <xref rid="Equ11" ref-type="" class="xref">7</xref>,
    <disp-formula id="Equ52" class="disp-formula">
     <label class="label">7</label>
     <alternatives class="alternatives">
      <tex-math id="M157" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$ {P}_i\frac{u_A}{u_{y_i^c}}={q}^{NP}+{q}_T\left({T}_i^{NP}-{A}_i^{NP}\right)\Rightarrow {T}_i^{NP}={A}_i^{NP}+\frac{\alpha {Y}_i-{q}^{NP}}{q_T^{NP}} $$\end{document}</tex-math>
      <div id="M158" display="block" class="math" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
       <div class="msub">
        <span class="mi">P</span>
        <span class="mi">i</span>
       </div>
       <div class="mfrac">
