   <p id="Par96" class="p">Turning to the social planner without permit market (denoted by superscript S), the equilibrium condition Eq. 
    <xref rid="Equ17" ref-type="" class="xref">11</xref> translates into
    <disp-formula id="Equ53" class="disp-formula">
     <label class="label">37</label>
     <alternatives class="alternatives">
      <tex-math id="M159" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$ \frac{\sum_{\kern0.28em j=1}^{\kern0.28em n}{P}_j{u}_A^j}{u_{y_i^c}}={MC}_i^S\Rightarrow \alpha {P}_w{y}_i^c=-c\ln \left[1-\frac{A_i^S}{E_i\left(1-{r}_i\right)}\right]\Rightarrow {A}_i^S={E}_i\left(1-{r}_i\right)\left(1-\exp \left(-\alpha {P}_w{y}_i^c/c\right)\right) $$\end{document}</tex-math>
      <div id="M160" display="block" class="math" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
       <div class="mfrac">
        <div class="mrow">
         <div class="munderover">
          <span class="mo">∑</span>
          <div class="mrow">
           <span width="thickmathspace" class="mspace"/>
           <span class="mi">j</span>
           <span class="mo">=</span>
           <span class="mn">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mrow">
           <span width="thickmathspace" class="mspace"/>
           <span class="mi">n</span>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="msub">
          <div class="mrow">
           <span class="mi">P</span>
          </div>
          <span class="mi">j</span>
         </div>
         <div class="msubsup">
          <div class="mrow">
           <span class="mi">u</span>
          </div>
          <span class="mi">A</span>
          <span class="mi">j</span>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="msub">
         <span class="mi">u</span>
         <div class="mrow">
          <div class="msubsup">
           <span class="mi">y</span>
           <span class="mi">i</span>
           <span class="mi">c</span>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <span class="mo">=</span>
       <div class="msubsup">
        <div class="mrow">
         <span class="mi">M</span>
         <span class="mi">C</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mi">i</span>
        <span class="mi">S</span>
       </div>
       <span stretchy="false" class="mo">⇒</span>
       <span class="mi">α</span>
       <div class="msub">
        <div class="mrow">
         <span class="mi">P</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mi">w</span>
       </div>
       <div class="msubsup">
        <div class="mrow">
         <span class="mi">y</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mi">i</span>
        <span class="mi">c</span>
       </div>
       <span class="mo">=</span>
       <span class="mo">−</span>
       <span class="mi">c</span>
       <span class="mi">ln</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mo">[</span>
        <span class="mn">1</span>
        <span class="mo">−</span>
        <div class="mfrac">
         <div class="msubsup">
          <span class="mi">A</span>
          <span class="mi">i</span>
          <span class="mi">S</span>
         </div>
         <div class="mrow">
          <div class="msub">
           <span class="mi">E</span>
           <span class="mi">i</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mrow">
